{"tid":1416802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔想分化但不吐不快] 和理非今次三擺既組織力和行動力不足","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T02:32:59.000Z","uid":37232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3173946fd0947f7024315709aa4f11cca223b190","tid":1416802,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:35:14.000Z","msg":"和理非今次三擺既組織力和行動力不足<br />\n導致除航空系統外, 其他行業的運作如常<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔該多D團結周圍的反政府人士, 到足夠人時, 因應情況揀一至兩個適合自己群組既行動去進行. e.g. 連儂牆<br />\n你地要記住, 只要守法既你地都係唔洗付極大成本去做, 你地做既絕對可以幫其他同路人減壓, 甚至可以開闢新戰線<br />\n<br />\n仲有, 長期宣傳只有和理非先係最適合, 因為和理非論述較武勇易入口<br />\n<br />\n細良今日呢兩條片建議睇睇, 武勇同和理非缺一不可, 共勉之<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QOXpQIMihME\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQOXpQIMihME&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=75239c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QOXpQIMihME</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ynPLtdis0hA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FynPLtdis0hA&d=ERzkPk9H60tcRIh4HMRTrv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=952d8964\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ynPLtdis0hA</a>"},{"pid":"5164eb4be1be31ce771f404c1f6f844d75a372ff","tid":1416802,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6997de574851ae35eb77797aaa785cbcbf98cc86","tid":1416802,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:36:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8480eff6b2ab4bbfbc2e8c73bb14aec29dba4ca0","tid":1416802,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"23ffbc306edd54383c2758567400764f9882c1ec","tid":1416802,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bbadc4641b3be3cc576218d58fe6e511be7f8eb","tid":1416802,"uid":156791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:37:38.000Z","msg":"唔關和理非事  